<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="" size="2">Hello {!Contact.FirstName},&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2">Thank you for your time today. Per our conversation, I wanted to get the information we discussed to you in writing.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b>The Goal of Fleet One EDGE</b> is to provide a high-value proposition for our trucking customers and our merchants that opt-in to the EDGE Network. In short, merchants that participate in the Fleet One EDGE Network agree to terms to offer competitive discounts on fuel at their locations to EDGE Customers.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="" size="2"><b style="">We will drive more business to {!Lead.Company}&nbsp;locations</b> by leveraging discounted pricing and promoting it on a daily basis to EDGE Customers. The discounted pricing at {!Lead.Company}&nbsp;locations will be completely visible to all EDGE customers and competitive enough to attract new fuel purchases to your locations. You will find that EDGE Customers will <b>pass up competitor locations</b> in order to fuel at your locations.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><u>Discount Details</u></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b>EDGE Customers will receive discounted pricing at your locations. We propose:</b></font></div><div style=""><ul style=""><li style=""><font face="arial" size="2">The discount to the EDGE customer will be Cost+ / Retail (-) (better of) at your discretion.</font></li><li style=""><font size="2" style=""><font face="arial">As an example, if you opted for a Cost Plus 6/Retail minus 5 (better of), then the Fleet One settlement for <b>EDGE Accounts Only</b>&nbsp;(with the merchant) would be Cost Plus $0.04 / Retail Minus $0.03 to account for our $0.02 per gallon marketing fee. As you determine the discount you would like to offer please keep the 2 cent marketing fee in mind. <span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></font></font></li></ul></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><u>Marketing</u></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><font size="2">Your locations will be highlighted as new locations to the EDGE Network in our daily price feed emails to the fleets. Not only will they see your newly discounted prices daily, but we will have a section of that email dedicated to your locations for 2 to 3 weeks.</font></li><li><font size="2">Inclusion for ongoing price feed promotions or targeted promotions may be possible.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></li><li><font size="2">New mobile app coming soon. This will allow fleets to pull up prices along their routes and target your locations as fuel destinations.&nbsp;</font></li></ul></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><u>The Benefits</u></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li style=""><font size="2">Your locations will acquire new incremental business and acquire repeat customers.</font></li><li style=""><font size="2">Statistics show that C-Store purchases will increase dramatically.&nbsp;</font></li><li style=""><font size="2">You have access to our marketing initiatives as discussed above.&nbsp;</font></li><li style=""><font size="2">An easy way to grow your business without any upfront costs. We only make money if you make money.&nbsp;</font></li></ul><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2">The next step is completing our Merchant Enrollment form. Let me know when you are ready for me to send that your way.&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: small;">I will follow up with you in a few days if I haven't heard back. Should you have any further questions, please don't hesitate to contact me.&nbsp;</span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2">Thank you for your time. We look forward to having you as part of the EDGE merchant network.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><b>Adam Aurich &nbsp;</b>| &nbsp;Fleet One EDGEâ€”Merchant Sales</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: small;">P: 844.480.EDGE &nbsp;| &nbsp;C: 801.547.7946</span></div><div style=""><font size="2">benefits@fleetoneedge.com</font></div><div style=""><font size="2">www.fleetoneedge.com</font></div><div style=""><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></div></div>]]></td>
